{"tid":1035283,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【六四30年】紀念碑美國LA建成 創作者望世人不要遺忘","createTime":"2019-02-24T14:05:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T06:51:08.000Z","uid":226955,"like":41,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"924fd80a4d6ee8850a400f8337ba52deba9099b7","tid":1035283,"uid":226955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T14:05:09.000Z","msg":"全球最大的六四紀念碑在美國洛杉磯落成，近200名各界人士到場參與落成儀式。紀念碑的創作者、雕塑家陳維明稱，「我們不想遺忘30年前發生在六四的慘案，那是中國人心中的傷痛」。<br />\n<br />\n六四紀念碑座落在連接洛杉磯與拉斯維加斯的15號州際公路，由「6」「4」兩個巨型數字組成，基座背面則刻有由天安門母親丁子霖收集的200多名六四死難者名字。陳維明表示，「<span style=\"color: red;\">這個雕塑本身高6.4米，加上2.5米的基座，剛好是8.9米，含義就是紀念89六四。這個公園離中國北京剛好是6,400英里，方位傾角是64度。</span>」<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n對於樹立雕塑的目的，陳維明稱他們想以雕塑方式，保持人們對六四事件的記憶，並提醒世人永遠不要忘記中共獨裁政權的威脅。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter/美國之音<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dhmDoox.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdhmDoox.png&h=e54d29e1&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f84c364153171aa86bc95556092b151e09f2680b","tid":1035283,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T14:05:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"517ceec5b1219cf877da54c3dd6962409bd522a3","tid":1035283,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T14:06:24.000Z","msg":"呢張相肯定被封鎖<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53490eea3146024241b57b463da71d007dd22f5f","tid":1035283,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-24T14:07:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32d02456a820cb88195b6d7da4f2e85000eac74f","